Getting a clear, organized view of your day just got a whole lot easier with
Todoist's new real-time, two-way Google Calendar integration.

You can now view, edit, and create Todoist tasks inside your Google Calendar
and vice versa – no need to flip between the two apps when scheduling your
events and tasks.

  * Want to move a task to tomorrow without leaving Google Calendar? Drag it over and it will be updated in Todoist. 
  * Need to book a meeting on Monday? Add an event in Google Calendar and it will be automatically added to your Todoist. 
  * Planning out a big project with lots of deadlines? List out all the tasks in Todoist, then see the full timeline neatly laid out in your calendar. 

Learn more about how the new integration can save you time, then get started
in just a few minutes:

